channel.title: Kobra - ‘Yellow Roses For Her...’. [Trap]
channel.description:
Kobra - ‘Yellow Roses For Her...’. [Trap]
Literally finished this in one day, something simple yet melodic. I’m still working on my music theory and thanks to Auxy, I’ve been able to practice for years now. This is the first music I’ll post after 2 years of my release, a remix from Phluze’s samples sound in Intonation. I hope you guys enjoy and thanks for the support!
https://soundcloud.app.goo.gl/VKHvxjU3mDtV8o477 That’ll be link to it
